
Steps:

    * mysql -uroot -p
      mysql>CREATE DATABASE Foorum;
      mysql>exit;
      mysql -uroot -p Foorum < Foorum.sql
    * cp foorum.yml foorum_local.yml
    * vi foorum_local.yml and change the 'dsn_pwd' config etc.
    * perl Makefile.PL; make; make test;
    * run `perl bin/foorum_server.pl` to test